00:39:37,500 --> 00:39:39,380
with some fresh ideas...

895
00:39:39,380 --> 00:39:41,220
Mr. Wen, we're off the clock.

896
00:39:41,820 --> 00:39:43,580
Since you're treating me to dinner,

897
00:39:43,780 --> 00:39:45,180
can we not talk about work?

898
00:39:46,860 --> 00:39:49,100
