to talk about work.

899
00:39:49,620 --> 00:39:51,300
If we're not talking about work,
then you're buying.

900
00:39:51,300 --> 00:39:51,860
Alright.

901
00:39:54,740 --> 00:39:55,940
No haggling with me?

902
00:40:00,060 --> 00:40:00,620
Fine.

903
00:40:03,220 --> 00:40:06,940
You were better
when you were stingy and money-obsessed.

904
00:40:09,300 --> 00:40:10,660
Focused only on your career.

905
00:40:10,660 --> 00:40:12,340
No feelings, no distractions.

906
00:40:13,300 --> 00:40:14,340
But now?

907
00:40:14,700 --> 00:40:17,300
How am I supposed
to trust you with my work?

908
00:40:17,860 --> 00:40:19,300
I know what you mean.

909
00:40:19,540 --> 00:40:20,260
But Mr. Wen,

910
00:40:20,740 --> 00:40:22,380
there are things in this world

911
00:40:22,380 --> 00:40:23,620
more valuable than money.

912
00:40:24,740 --> 00:40:25,940
Don't tell me you mean love.

913
00:40:27,220 --> 00:40:28,380
Love is one of them.

914
00:40:31,900 --> 00:40:35,940
Looks like Mr. Xia's got you
all turned around.

915
00:40:36,580 --> 00:40:37,260
Don't even bring him up.

916
00:40:37,420 --> 00:40:38,860
I haven't seen him for a long time.

917
00:40:41,260 --> 00:40:43,660
I thought you were

918
00:40:43,660 --> 00:40:44,780
burning with desire.

919
00:40:45,260 --> 00:40:45,860
What happened?

920
00:40:45,900 --> 00:40:46,820
He's too busy.

921
00:40:47,860 --> 00:40:49,420
I haven't seen him

922
00:40:49,660 --> 00:40:51,060
since that day on Nanjing Road.

923
00:40:51,620 --> 00:40:52,620
That was over a month ago.

924
00:40:54,180 --> 00:40:54,860
What's keeping him so busy?

925
00:40:55,780 --> 00:40:56,980
I don't know the specifics.

926
00:40:59,020 --> 00:41:00,180
He probably doesn't
want to see you, right?

927
00:41:03,620 --> 00:41:05,740
He's working on things
that serve the greater good.

928
00:41:06,020 --> 00:41:06,620
Is that so?

929
00:41:07,540 --> 00:41:08,540
Since you haven't seen
each other for so long,

930
00:41:08,540 --> 00:41:09,660
wouldn't that affect your relationship?

931
00:41:09,660 --> 00:41:10,380
Not really.

932
00:41:11,820 --> 00:41:12,540
So sure?

933
00:41:13,980 --> 00:41:15,060
Let me put it this way.

934
00:41:16,060 --> 00:41:16,980
He and I

935
00:41:17,860 --> 00:41:19,380
may go years without seeing each other,

936
00:41:20,460 --> 00:41:23,260
or even without knowing
if the other is still alive.

937
00:41:23,940 --> 00:41:26,740
But when we meet again,

938
00:41:28,180 --> 00:41:29,220
it'll be just like before.

939
00:41:29,220 --> 00:41:29,900
Got somewhere to be?

940
00:41:30,740 --> 00:41:32,740
Or is it boring to talk about me?

941
00:41:33,700 --> 00:41:34,580
It's not boring,

942
00:41:34,580 --> 00:41:35,900
