943
00:41:37,380 --> 00:41:40,220
Since we sat down,

944
00:41:40,220 --> 00:41:41,860
you've checked your watch three times.

945
00:41:42,820 --> 00:41:43,780
You're clearly up to something.

946
00:41:45,420 --> 00:41:46,420
Is it a date?

947
00:41:47,980 --> 00:41:48,660
Who is it?

948
00:41:50,100 --> 00:41:50,980
Is it a girl?

949
00:41:51,260 --> 00:41:52,020
Is she pretty?

950
00:41:53,300 --> 00:41:54,140
Prettier than you.

951
00:41:55,980 --> 00:41:56,980
How long have you known each other?

952
00:41:57,940 --> 00:41:59,020
Not long.

953
00:42:01,300 --> 00:42:03,580
You keep dodging the topic.

954
00:42:04,740 --> 00:42:05,380
Are you into her?

955
00:42:06,820 --> 00:42:08,580
So you get to be head over heels,
but I can't fall for someone?

956
00:42:08,740 --> 00:42:10,100
No, I'm happy for you.

957
00:42:12,100 --> 00:42:13,020
It's about time.

958
00:42:13,060 --> 00:42:13,820
I'm leaving.

959
00:42:13,980 --> 00:42:15,300
Alright, go ahead.

960
00:42:16,060 --> 00:42:17,540
Hope it all works out between you two.

961
00:42:18,380 --> 00:42:19,740
Hope you meet up again soon.

962
00:42:20,060 --> 00:42:20,620
Okay.

963
00:42:25,620 --> 00:42:26,980
He's got a date,
but still asked me to dinner...

964
00:42:28,020 --> 00:42:29,380
